# SFIT Topological Dome Validation — CeRu₄Sn₆

This repository contains experimental data, analysis scripts, and reproducibility resources for testing the **SFIT (Symbolic Field Interpretation Theory)** prediction of a *topological dome* in the anomalous Hall conductivity of **CeRu₄Sn₆**.

---

